{"tid":2376444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子終於來臨","createTime":"2021-01-22T21:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T22:54:17.000Z","uid":285559,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24e4d4c3ef3408db007534b5265121ceff144889","tid":2376444,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:07:24.000Z","msg":"佐敦封城又好，全港宵禁又好，有咩事發生都唔驚，只要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n<br />\n當然，到有日真係出現全香港範圍MAP炮就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=fc554873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放喺廚房櫃嘅罐頭同米，米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿，到中國午餐肉，回煱肉，豆，菜，金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=bb698acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開，太多，放到出廳 [依啲全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=61f1bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染，未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐，依家啲水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即食麵 有5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無嘢買嘅日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待手持午餐肉就可以有閪屌嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5473523283827dad9318935a091818d77fa405","tid":2376444,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:26:17.000Z","msg":"高登仔先知先覺"},{"pid":"6dc2ff65d89b7f4393df2a000d6d2fc8ec09ef4f","tid":2376444,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:27:47.000Z","msg":"樓豬食開中國牛餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e7bb0188aabb012b981bb81d5c1ea539d0b7f0","tid":2376444,"uid":66557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:32:07.000Z","msg":"喂你啲午餐肉過撚曬期啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70d962c78834b8a0c3ebcb2f98e4941d9a13b59","tid":2376444,"uid":282031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47e7bb0188aabb012b981bb81d5c1ea539d0b7f0","tid":2376444,"uid":66557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:32:07.000Z","msg":"喂你啲午餐肉過撚曬期啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:34:25.000Z","msg":"批午餐肉放左8年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528bc60f4b0d367e8fd421c1feed2acd01869054","tid":2376444,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5473523283827dad9318935a091818d77fa405","tid":2376444,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:26:17.000Z","msg":"高登仔先知先覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T22:54:17.000Z","msg":"高登萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}